# Git Rules

## Push Policy
- NEVER run `git push` without explicit user approval
- Always provide a brief change summary before commit

## Commit Messages
- Meaningful messages in Russian
- Format: `[type] Brief description`
- Types: `feat`, `fix`, `docs`, `refactor`, `test`, `chore`
- Example: `feat: –Ф–Њ–±–∞–≤–ї–µ–љ–∞ —В—А–∞–љ—Б–Ї—А–Є–±–∞—Ж–Є—П –≥–Њ–ї–Њ—Б–Њ–≤—Л—Е —Б–Њ–Њ–±—Й–µ–љ–Є–є`

## Branches
- `main` вАФ stable version
- `dev` вАФ development
- `feature/*` вАФ new features
- `bugfix/*` вАФ fixes

## Deploy
- Never deploy to production/staging without explicit user permission
- All deploy commands require confirmation
